/* City of Lakes */Thane is also Known as City of lakes.  There are many other lakes in Thane such as Kachrali, Makhmali talao, Upvan Lake and 20+ others.
Kachrali Talao (Marathi : कचराळी तलाव) is a lake located in Thane, Maharashtra, India. It also has a temple of Ganapati on it's shore.
